                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Event \"Sentuhan Cahaya Rembulan\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/06/140615443/88720f88d2fd832026a898c1de4cd004_8787376314338621196.png"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "30 Agustus 2021",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Selama event berlangsung, selesaikan misi di \"Kisah Moonchase\" atau ikuti event \"Pemburu Cahaya Rembulan\" dan tantangan \"Jejak Kuliner\", untuk mendapatkan Claymore Eksklusif \"Luxurious Sea-Lord\" dan Material Refinement-nya, Crown of Insight, Primogem, resep, serta hadiah lainnya.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
